'''羅莎琳·富蘭克林號'''（Rosalind Franklin）,<ref name="BBC-20190207">{{cite news |last=Amos |first=Jonathan |title=Rosalind Franklin: Mars rover named after DNA pioneer |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-47151778 |date=7 February 2019 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |access-date=7 February 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109081803/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-47151778 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 原名火星地外生物探測車（ExoMars rover）, 是一輛計劃中的火星車，它是[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]和[[俄羅斯航太|俄羅斯航太]]合作的[[ExoMars|火星地外生物探索]]專案的組成部分<ref name="Vago">{{cite journal |url=http://esamultimedia.esa.int/multimedia/publications/ESA-Bulletin-155/offline/download.pdf |title=ExoMars: ESA's Next Step in Mars Exploration |journal=Bulletin |publisher=歐洲太空總署 |first1=Jorge |last1=Vago |first2=Olivier |last2=Witasse |first3=Pietro |last3=Baglioni |first4=Albert |last4=Haldemann |first5=Giacinto |last5=Gianfiglio |first6=Thierry |last6=Blancquaert |first7=Don |last7=McCoy |first8=Rolf |last8=de Groot |display-authors=5 |issue=155 |pages=12–23 |date=2013年8月 |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2018-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181024142601/http://esamultimedia.esa.int/multimedia/publications/ESA-Bulletin-155/offline/download.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AP-20140327">{{cite news |url=http://apnews.excite.com/article/20140327/DACQ6UHG0.html |title=2018 mission: Mars rover prototype unveiled in UK |work=Excite.com |agency=Associated Press |last=Katz |first=Gregory |date=2014-03-27 |access-date=2014-03-29 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407083253/http://apnews.excite.com/article/20140327/DACQ6UHG0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。羅莎琳·富蘭克林號原定於2020年7月發射<ref name="LaunchMoved2020">{{cite press release |url=http://www.esa.int/For_Media/Press_Releases/Second_ExoMars_mission_moves_to_next_launch_opportunity_in_2020 |title=Second ExoMars mission moves to next launch opportunity in 2020 |publisher=European Space Agency |date=2 May 2016 |access-date=2 May 2016 |archive-date=2016-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502194618/http://www.esa.int/For_Media/Press_Releases/Second_ExoMars_mission_moves_to_next_launch_opportunity_in_2020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但後來被推遲到2022年<ref name="LaunchMoved2022">{{cite press release |url=http://www.esa.int/Newsroom/Press_Releases/ExoMars_to_take_off_for_the_Red_Planet_in_2022 |title=N° 6–2020: ExoMars to take off for the Red Planet in 2022 |publisher=[[ESA|ESA]] |date=2020-03-12 |access-date=2020-03-12 |archive-date=2021-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330014823/https://www.esa.int/Newsroom/Press_Releases/ExoMars_to_take_off_for_the_Red_Planet_in_2022 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。  

一旦成功登陸[[火星|火星]]，羅莎琳·富蘭克林號將和俄羅斯的{{Link-en|哥薩克舞登陸器|Kazachok}}（又譯：小[[哥薩克|哥薩克]]登陸器）分離，並開始為期七個月的探測任務，其目標是尋找火星過去存在[[火星生命|生命]]的依據。[[火星微量氣體任務衛星|火星微量氣體任務衛星]]將作為羅莎琳·富蘭克林號和哥薩克舞登陸器的信號傳遞衛星。

羅莎琳·富蘭克林號以[[英國|英國]]物理化學家[[羅莎琳·富蘭克林|羅莎琳·富蘭克林]]命名。

