===設計===
羅莎琳·富蘭克林號火星車是一輛六輪[[太陽能光伏|太陽能光伏]]探測車，質量大約是300公斤，約比2004年的[[火星探測漫遊者|火星探測漫遊者]]火星車[[勇氣號|勇氣號]]和[[機遇號|機遇號]]重60%<ref name="mepag.jpl.nasa.gov">{{Cite conference |url=http://mepag.jpl.nasa.gov/meeting/mar-09/09_ExoMars_Status_MEPAG_09_Final.pdf |title=ExoMars Status |conference=20th Mars Exploration Program Analysis Group Meeting. 3–4 March 2009. Arlington, Virginia. |publisher=歐洲太空總署|first1=J. L. |last1=Vego |display-authors=etal |year=2009 |access-date=2009-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409170116/http://mepag.jpl.nasa.gov/meeting/mar-09/09_ExoMars_Status_MEPAG_09_Final.pdf |archive-date=2009-04-09}}</ref>，但只有後來的[[好奇號|好奇號]]及[[毅力號火星探測器|毅力號火星探測器]]質量的三分之一。

羅莎琳·富蘭克林號將搭載一台可鑽地2米的樣本採集鑽孔機以及分析實驗室抽屜（{{lang-en|Analytical Laboratory Drawer}}、ALD），支援「巴斯德酬載」科學儀器。它將尋找過去生命的[[生物分子|生物分子]]或[[生物標記|生物標記]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://exploration.esa.int/mars/45787-rover-surface-operations/|title=Rover surface operations|publisher=歐洲太空總署|date=2012-12-18|access-date=2012-03-16|archive-date=2018-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026064601/http://exploration.esa.int/mars/45787-rover-surface-operations/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Astro2017">{{cite journal |title=Habitability on Early Mars and the Search for Biosignatures with the ExoMars Rover |journal=Astrobiology|first=Jorge L. |last=Vago |display-authors=etal |volume=17 |issue=6–7 |pages=471–510 |date=2017年7月 |doi=10.1089/ast.2016.1533 |pmid=31067287 |bibcode=2017AsBio..17..471V|pmc=5685153 }}</ref><ref name="Press-Info">{{cite press release |url=https://www.thalesgroup.com/en/content/press-info-exomars-status |title=Press Info: ExoMars Status |publisher=Thales Group |date=2012-05-08|access-date=2012-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203010438/https://www.thalesgroup.com/en/content/press-info-exomars-status |archive-date=2013-12-03}}</ref><ref name="Instruments">{{cite web |url=http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/ExoMars/SEMSZIAMS7F_0.html |title=The ExoMars Instruments |publisher=European Space Agency |date=2008-02-01|access-date=2012-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026132118/http://www.esa.int/SPECIALS/ExoMars/SEMSZIAMS7F_0.html |archive-date=26 October 2012}}</ref><ref name="still keen">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-17390576 |title=Europe still keen on Mars missions |work=BBC News |first=Jonathan |last=Amos |date=2012-03-15 |access-date=2012-03-16 |archive-date=2020-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200106003311/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-17390576 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===建造===
羅莎琳·富蘭克林號的主要製造方[[空中巴士國防航天|空中巴士國防航天]]英國分部從2014年3月開始就積極地獲取關鍵的零部件<ref name='closing $ gap'>{{cite news |first=Stephen |last=Clark |title=Facing funding gap, ExoMars rover is on schedule for now |date=2014-03-03 |url=http://www.spaceflightnow.com/news/n1403/03exomars/ |work=Spaceflight Now |access-date=2014-03-03 |archive-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209232327/https://spaceflightnow.com/news/n1403/03exomars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年12月探測車的經費獲得[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]成員國的批准<ref name="Funding 2nd launch">{{cite news |url=https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/wireStory/europe-agrees-fund-ariane-orbital-launcher-27307058 |title=Europe Agrees to Fund Ariane 6 Orbital Launcher |work=ABC News |agency=Associated Press |location=Berlin, Germany |date=2014-12-02 |access-date=2014-12-02 |archive-date=2020-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310110945/https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/wireStory/europe-agrees-fund-ariane-orbital-launcher-27307058 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但因為資金不足原定的發射時間被推遲到2020年<ref name="Delaying 2018">{{cite news |url=http://www.industryweek.com/emerging-technologies/money-troubles-may-delay-europe-russia-mars-mission |title=Money Troubles May Delay Europe-Russia Mars Mission |work=Industry Week |agency=Agence France-Presse |date=2016-01-15 |access-date=2016-01-16 |archive-date=2020-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201184900/http://www.industryweek.com/emerging-technologies/money-troubles-may-delay-europe-russia-mars-mission |dead-url=no }}</ref>。探測車的輪子和[[懸吊系統|懸吊系統]]由加拿大MDA公司製造，費用則由[[加拿大太空總署|加拿大太空總署]]支付<ref name='closing $ gap'/>。每個輪子的直徑為{{cvt|25|cm|in}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.planetary.org/blogs/emily-lakdawalla/2019/esa-prepares-for-2020-launch.html|title=ESA Prepares for ExoMars Rover 2020 Launch at Mars and on Earth.|work=Emily Lakdawalla, ''The Planetary Society''|access-date=2019-05-30|archive-date=2019-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802234955/http://www.planetary.org/blogs/emily-lakdawalla/2019/esa-prepares-for-2020-launch.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[俄羅斯航太|俄羅斯航太]]負責提供在夜間給電子元件保溫的[[放射性同位素加熱器|放射性同位素加熱器]]<ref name=Vago/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.russianspaceweb.com/exomars_2016.html |title=ExoMars-2016 mission |website=Russianspaceweb.com |first=Anatoly |last=Zak |date=2016-07-28 |access-date=2018-05-15 |quote=In 2018, a Russian-built radioactive heat generator would be installed on the ExoMars rover, along with possible suit of Russian instruments. |archive-date=2013-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023061238/http://www.russianspaceweb.com/exomars_2016.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2018年到2019年間，羅莎琳·富蘭克林號由空中巴士國防航天在英國組裝完成<ref>{{cite news |url=https://spaceflightnow.com/2019/08/28/exomars-rover-leaves-british-factory-heads-for-testing-in-france/ |title=ExoMars rover leaves British factory, heads for testing in France |work=Spaceflight Now |date=2019-08-28 |first=Stephen |last=Clark |accessdate=2021-03-11 |archive-date=2019-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204124530/https://spaceflightnow.com/2019/08/28/exomars-rover-leaves-british-factory-heads-for-testing-in-france/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===發射時間===
2020年3月因為降落傘測試的問題歐洲太空總署將發射時間推遲到2022年8月到10月間<ref name="LaunchMoved2022" />，之後發射時間又被調整到從2022年9月20日開始的為期12天的發射窗口<ref name="esa-20201001" />。2022年3月17日，受[[2022年俄罗斯入侵乌克兰|俄乌冲突]]影响，欧洲航天局宣布终止与俄罗斯合作，其中包括将要携带罗莎琳·富兰克林号前往火星的[[ExoMars|ExoMars]]任务。<ref>{[cite web|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/530766824_115479|title=欧洲航天局终止与俄罗斯合作，俄方回应：将独立完成火星任务 }}</ref>

===命名===
2018年7月歐洲太空總署向公眾徵求探測車的名字<ref>{{cite news |url=http://fortune.com/2018/07/20/name-european-space-agency-exomars-rover/ |title=Want to Name the Next European Mars Rover? Here's Your Chance |work=Fortune |first=Renae |last=Reints |date=2018-07-20 |access-date=2018-07-20 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029182239/https://fortune.com/2018/07/20/name-european-space-agency-exomars-rover/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年2月7日ExoMars探測車被命名為羅莎琳·富蘭克林號以紀念對[[DNA|DNA]]、[[RNA|RNA]]、[[病毒|病毒]]、[[煤炭|煤炭]]和[[石墨|石墨]]的分子結構研究做出卓越貢獻的英國女科學家[[羅莎琳·富蘭克林|羅莎琳·富蘭克林]]（1920年－1958年）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/government/news/name-of-british-built-mars-rover-revealed|title=Name of British built Mars rover revealed|website=GOV.UK|language=en|access-date=2019-02-07|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920100132/https://www.gov.uk/government/news/name-of-british-built-mars-rover-revealed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

